g 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/AvrilLavigneWarpedTour-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/AvrilLavigneWarpedTour-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/AvrilLavigneWarpedTour-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a>将于今年在Warped Tour上首次亮相。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/avril-lavigne-live-at-glastonbury-2024-setlist-review-photos-3770749">Avril Lavigne Live on Glastonbury 2024：Pop-Punk Star提供了无羞于的怀旧节</a></strong></li></ul><p>“ SK8ER BOI”艺术家将在Vans赞助的活动的一个地点演出，该活动将于2025年返回六年来的第一版。</p><p>拉维尼（Lavigne）计划在6月14日至15日之间在RFK体育场的城市节日场地上出现，她在阵容中与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/3oh3">3OH！3之</a>类的阵容中展出，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bowling-for-soup">保龄球，供应汤</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beauty-school-dropout">美容学校辍学，辍学</a>， 408，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fever-333">发烧333</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/of-mice-and-men">老鼠和男性</a>。</p><p>这位歌手兼作曲家在视频公告中分享了这一消息，在录像带中，她收到了一个蛋糕，揭示了磨损的巡回演出日期。 “扭曲的旅行回来了！”拉维尼说。 “没错，让我们庆祝。 DC很快见。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DF8fXURPY09/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex